[00:46.50]Enhanced LRC format
[00:51.00]Supports word-level timing
[00:55.50]For better synchronization
[01:00.00]With the music

[01:04.50]Different players
[01:09.00]May support different features
[01:13.50]Of the LRC format
[01:18.00]Check your player's documentation

[01:22.50]Time format variations:
[01:27.00][mm:ss.xx] - Standard format
[01:31.50][mm:ss:xx] - Alternative format
[01:36.00][mm:ss.xx0] - Extended precision
[01:40.50]All are valid LRC formats

[01:45.00]Metadata tags:
[01:49.50][ti:Title] - Song title
[01:54.00][ar:Artist] - Artist name
[01:58.50][al:Album] - Album name
[02:03.00][au:Author] - Songwriter
[02:07.50][length:mm:ss] - Song length
[02:12.00][by:Creator] - LRC creator
[02:16.50][offset:+/-ms] - Time offset
[02:21.00][re:Player] - Player software
[02:25.50][ve:version] - LRC version

[02:30.00]End of second song
